Lasius
=================================

Lasius is in the style of hamster a simple time booking and tracking platform and aims to provided 
an easy interface to book your daily work time on different projects/tasks.

The second goal of Lasius is to combine several different kind of techniques/architecture, all of 
used in their main scope:
- Eventsourcing -> All time booking operations
- BigPipe -> Integrate various content into dashboard page in one single request using chunked http transmition
